name: stable-baselines3
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "stable-baselines3" %}
{% set version = "1.4.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/stable_baselines3-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0d5219d473d6caa32e770174c65294e6111fcdfce3697a82a58d9100d9227f9f

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
  run:
    - cloudpickle
    - gym >=0.17,<0.20
    - matplotlib-base
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - python >=3.7
    - pytorch >=1.8.1

test:
  imports:
    - stable_baselines3
    - stable_baselines3.a2c
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/DLR-RM/stable-baselines3
  summary: Pytorch version of Stable Baselines, implementations of reinforcement learning algorithms.
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  doc_url: https://stable-baselines3.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/DLR-RM/stable-baselines3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cyprienc
